          "type": "text",
          "text": "USP_InvoiceContractLineAllocationRetrieve_AandA",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " is designed to retrieve invoice contract line allocations from a SQL Server database. It accepts various parameters to filter and log the retrieval process, and it handles both standard and split fiscal year invoices. The procedure logs its operations and any exceptions encountered during execution."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
